dataWork=data[["Patient_ID","Hour","O2Sat","FiO2"]]
mask=dataWork["O2Sat"].isnull() & dataWork["FiO2"].isnull()
dataWork=dataWork[~mask]
condNormal=(dataWork["O2Sat"] >= 95) & (dataWork["O2Sat"] <= 100)
condNormal1=(dataWork["O2Sat"] >= 90) & (dataWork["O2Sat"] < 95)
cond=(dataWork["O2Sat"] >= 85) & (dataWork["O2Sat"] < 90)
cond1=(dataWork["O2Sat"] >= 83) & (dataWork["O2Sat"] < 85)
cond2=(dataWork["O2Sat"] >= 80) & (dataWork["O2Sat"] < 83)
cond3=(dataWork["O2Sat"] >= 75) & (dataWork["O2Sat"] < 80)
cond4=(dataWork["O2Sat"] >= 0) & (dataWork["O2Sat"] < 75)
dataWork.loc[condNormal,'FiO2']= dataWork.loc[condNormal,'FiO2'].fillna(0.21)
dataWork.loc[condNormal1,'FiO2']= dataWork.loc[condNormal1,'FiO2'].fillna(0.23)
dataWork.loc[cond,'FiO2']= dataWork.loc[cond,'FiO2'].fillna(0.29)
dataWork.loc[cond1,'FiO2']= dataWork.loc[cond1,'FiO2'].fillna(0.44)
dataWork.loc[cond2,'FiO2']= dataWork.loc[cond2,'FiO2'].fillna(0.61)
dataWork.loc[cond3,'FiO2']= dataWork.loc[cond3,'FiO2'].fillna(0.81)
dataWork.loc[cond4,'FiO2']= dataWork.loc[cond4,'FiO2'].fillna(0.99)
dataWork["O2Sat"].fillna(method="ffill",inplace=True)
dataWork["FiO2"] = dataWork["FiO2"].apply(lambda x: x if x > 0.18 else 0.19)
dataWork["FiO2"] = dataWork["FiO2"].apply(lambda x: x if x < 1 else 1.0)

dataWork.to_csv("dataSetO2_version_1.csv",index=False)

def corr_matrix(df):
    corr = df.corr()
    mask = np.triu(np.ones_like(corr, dtype=bool))
    f, ax = plt.subplots(figsize=(42,42))
    cmap = sns.diverging_palette(220, 10, as_cmap=True)
    sns.heatmap(corr, mask=mask, cmap="Paired", vmax=.3, center=0,
              square=True, linewidths=.5, cbar_kws={"shrink": .5})
  
corr_matrix(df)

data = pd.read_csv("E:\Bhuvan\College\Datathon 2024\Project\Dataset\Dataset.csv")


data.drop(columns=data.columns[0], axis=1,  inplace=True)


septic_shock_patients=data['Patient_ID'][data['SepsisLabel']==1].unique()
septic_shock_patients


septic_df=data[data.Patient_ID.isin(septic_shock_patients)]


admitted_with_sepsis_patients=data['Patient_ID'][(data['SepsisLabel']==1) & (data['Hour']==0)]

admitted_with_sepsis_df=data[data.Patient_ID.isin(admitted_with_sepsis_patients)]


sepsis_after_adm_df=septic_df.merge(admitted_with_sepsis_df, how = 'outer' ,indicator=True).loc[lambda x : x['_merge']=='left_only']


non_septic_df = data.merge(septic_df, how = 'outer' ,indicator=True).loc[lambda x : x['_merge']=='left_only']


data['sepsisType']=np.nan


data.loc[data.Patient_ID.isin(admitted_with_sepsis_patients), 'sepsisType'] = 'SepsisBeforeAdm'


data.loc[data.Patient_ID.isin(septic_shock_patients) & data['sepsisType'].isnull(), 'sepsisType'] = 'SepsisAfterAdm'


data.loc[data['sepsisType'].isnull(), 'sepsisType'] = 'NonSepsis'
data['sepsisType'].value_counts()
data['sepsisType'].value_counts().plot.bar()

data['hasSIRS'].value_counts()

condition_HR=(data['HR']>90)
condition_Resp=(data['Resp']>20) |( data['PaCO2']<32)
condition_wbc=(data['WBC']>12000) |( data['WBC']<4000)

data['SIRS_Score']=np.where(condition_temp, 1, 0)+np.where(condition_HR, 1, 0)+np.where(condition_Resp, 1, 0)+np.where(condition_wbc, 1, 0)

import csv
import os

folder_path= r'E:\Bhuvan\College\Datathon 2024\Project\Dataset\training_setA'
txt_files = sorted(os.listdir(folder_path))

to_csv = []
df2=pd.DataFrame()
count=1
for file in range(0, len(txt_files)):
    path_name = os.path.join(folder_path, txt_files[file])
    to_csv.append(path_name)

for file in to_csv:
    with open(file) as f:
        df1 = pd.read_csv(f, delimiter='|')
        df1['PatientId']=count
        df2=df2.append([df1])
        count=count+1

def read_data(filepath,datatable):
    count = 0
    rows = 0
    for filename in os.listdir(filepath):
        if filename.endswith(".psv"): 
            with open(filepath + filename) as openfile:
                patient = filename.split("p")[1]
                patient = patient.split(".")[0]

                file = pd.read_csv(openfile,sep = "|")
                file['Patient_ID'] = patient
                
                file = file.reset_index()
                file = file.rename(columns={"index": "Hour"})
                
                datatable = datatable.append(file)
                
                rows += file.size
                count += 1
        # Print progress after 10k files
        if count % 10000 == 0:
            print("Progress || Files: {} || Number of items: {}".format(count,rows))
    print("Done ||| Files: {} || Number of items: {}".format(count,rows))
    return(datatable)

def read_data(basepath, df):
    for filename in os.listdir(basepath):
        if filename.endswith(".psv"): 
            filepath = os.path.join(basepath, filename) 
            with open(filepath) as openfile:
                patient = filename.split("p")[1]
                patient = patient.split(".")[0]
                temp_df = pd.read_csv(filepath, sep='|')  
                df = pd.concat([df, temp_df], ignore_index=True)
    return df
